Userfunc: (Name: UserFunc viraj-Sat Mar 28 02:06:31 PDT 2009-14 function: ci_pig_udfs.RegexGroupCount(&apos;www\\.yahoo&lt;br class=&quot;atl-forced-newline&quot; /&gt;.com/sports&apos;) Operator Key: viraj-Sat Mar 28 02:06:31 PDT 2009-14)&lt;br/&gt;
Userfunc fs: int&lt;br/&gt;
