Equality test false&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2009-03-28 02:06:43,923 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;main&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; INFO  org.apache.pig.backend.hadoop.executionengine.mapReduceLayer.MapReduceLauncher - 100% complete&lt;br/&gt;
2009-03-28 02:06:43,923 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;main&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; INFO  org.apache.pig.backend.hadoop.executionengine.mapReduceLayer.MapReduceLauncher - Success!&lt;br/&gt;
(0)&lt;br/&gt;
(0)&lt;br/&gt;
(0)&lt;br/&gt;
